<h2>Event Control Panel</h2>

<p>From here you can create the Events that occur in this Universe. Each
should have an objective description, preferably in the
<a href="http://fictionwriting.about.com/od/glossary/g/3rdperson.htm">third person</a>.
Each Character involved in an Event gets their own Experience, which may or
may not be an accurate depiction of what happened. Typically this should be written
in the
<a href="http://fictionwriting.about.com/od/glossary/g/firstperson.htm">first person</a>.
But exceptions could easily be made for the sake of telling a good story.</p>

